One user posted a photo of the controversial 3rd Battalion 5th Marines who posed with a Nazi SS flag.

And finally an account with the name Uncle Dad tweeted a picture of William Calley, the US officer who murdered 22 Vietnamese, adding: 'love you dad'.

Issa's team rushed to undo the retweets after receiving a wave of criticism.

A spokesman told the Daily Dot that Issa does not always control the account himself. 

